David Beckham's 40th birthday is on Saturday, 2 May . 
  He is expected to stay at the five-star luxury Amanjena resort, just outside Marrakech . 
  Tom Cruise, Guy Ritchie, Gordon Ramsay and best friend Dave Gardner are set to attend the bash . 
  The Beckhams have stayed at the resort before and renewed their vows there in 2004 . 
 